{
    "Txt_Name": "Card_4160005_3",
    "Dialogue": [
        {
            "index": 1,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "はぁ？\n除霊？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_001.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 2,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "お願い。\n祈祷で除霊して欲しい。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_002.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 3,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "何を言っている？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_003.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 4,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "私は祈祷師でも、陰陽師でもない。\nただの、お寺の娘。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_004.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 5,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "除霊の祈祷なんて、出来るわけがない。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_005.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 6,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "除霊出来なくてもいい。\n利恵が、除霊出来たと信じて、安心することが大切なの。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_006.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 7,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "ねぇ、今そこで聞いてたけどさ……、何でそこまでするの？\nどうして利恵に、そこまで尽くすの？ "
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_007.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 8,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "何でって、考えたこともない。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_008.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 9,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "考えたことがない…？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_009.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 10,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "これは呼吸と一緒なの。\n利恵がいて、私がいる。ただ、それだけ。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_010.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 11,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "利恵に降り掛かった災難は、\n同時に、私に降り掛かった災難でもあるの。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_011.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 12,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "つまり、今、霊に怯えてるのは、利恵であり、私。\nわかる？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_012.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 13,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "だからね。\nそんなふうに考えたことは、まったくない。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_013.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 14,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "……じゃあ、1つ教えて。\nもし……、もし、利恵がいなくなったら？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_014.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 15,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "えっ？\n利恵がいなくなる？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_015.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 16,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "つまりその……、利恵に万が一のことがあったら。\n鳴はどうする？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_016.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 17,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "そんなこと考えたくないけど。\nもし、そんな事があったら、思いっ切り泣くだろうね。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_017.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 18,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "泣くって、それだけ……？\nいや、後を追ってよからぬことを考えたり……。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_018.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 19,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "そうなってみないとわからないけど。\nでも、それは無いと思う。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_019.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 20,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "前に、父親に言われたことを思い出した。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_020.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 21,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "えっ？\nお父さん？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_021.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 22,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "うちはお寺だから、いろんな別れを見てきた。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_022.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 23,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "まぁ、そうでしょうね……。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_023.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 24,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "父親は私にこう言った。涙には、大きく分けて、2種類ある。\n自分を悲しむ涙と、相手を悲しむ涙。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_024.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 25,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "自分を悲しむ涙と、相手を悲しむ涙……？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_025.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 26,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "自分を悲しむ涙は、後悔の涙。\nもっと優しくすればよかった、もっと話をすればよかった。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_026.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 27,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "そういう、無念の涙。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_027.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 28,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "もう1つは、相手を悲しむ涙……。\n生前、亡くなった人のことを、十分に愛した人の涙。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_028.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 29,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "鳴の話を聞いてて、思い出した。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_029.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 30,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "……志穂。私からもお願いしていい？\n何か、祈祷っぽいことして、利恵を安心させてあげて。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_030.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 31,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "千紗さん……。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_031.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 32,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "鳴に、悔し涙を流させるわけにいかないからさー……。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_032.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 33,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "わかった。\nそれっぽくやってみる。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_033.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 34,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "2人とも、ありがとう。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_034.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 35,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "んんんんん、ハッ！！"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_035.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 36,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "えー……、以上。\n除霊の祈祷終了。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_036.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 37,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "ありがとう。\nこれでもう、霊はいない？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_037.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 38,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "もう、心配無用。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_038.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 39,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "利恵、よかったね！"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_039.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 40,
            "heroineId": [
                13
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "丸山利恵"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "本当に、もう大丈夫……？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_040.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 41,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "大丈夫ですよね？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_041.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 42,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "大丈夫。\nたぶん。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_042.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 43,
            "heroineId": [
                13
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "丸山利恵"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "でも、どうして志穂が除霊なんて出来るの？\nただの、お寺の娘なのに。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_043.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 44,
            "heroineId": [
                3
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "鹿野志穂"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "だよね。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_044.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 45,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "それは……、たくさんの死者と向かい合ってるからよ。\nほら！　お寺って霊の数も多そうじゃない。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_045.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 46,
            "heroineId": [
                13
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "丸山利恵"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "そういうもの……？"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_046.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 47,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "とにかく！　これでもう心配いらないよ。\nそれに、もしまた何か困ったことがあっても……。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_047.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 48,
            "heroineId": [
                6
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "赤川千紗"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "利恵には、鳴がついてるから大丈夫！\nだよね？　鳴。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_048.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 49,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "うん。\nいつでも私は側にいる。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_049.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 50,
            "heroineId": [
                13
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "丸山利恵"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "……ありがとう。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_050.mp3"
        },
        {
            "index": 51,
            "heroineId": [
                16
            ],
            "name": {
                "default": "遠見鳴"
            },
            "message": {
                "default": "さ、そろそろライブの準備に取り掛かろう。\n利恵と一緒のライブ、ふふっ。"
            },
            "voice": "card/Card_16/Card_4160005_3/card_4160005_3_051.mp3"
        }
    ]
}